[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black 1 is the solution, probably this problem wouldn't even be published.
\par After White 2 and Black 3, White's throw-in at 4 is a maek which makes use of the special character of the corner.
\par
\par At the end, Black is captured with the sequence up to 6.
\par }
