Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Whenever White threw-in Black was captured. Therefore Black shouldn't let that happen.
\par
\par \cf1\b The opponent's vital point is my vital point.\cf0\b0
\par
\par Black's connection at 1 looks ordinary but it is a \cf1\b brilliant move\cf0\b0 .
\par White can't win the capturing race anymore.
\par
\par }
